Date: 1997-10-09

Title: Collective Dynamics of Solitons and Inequivalent Quantizations

Authors: Juan Pedro Garrahan and Martin Kruczenski

Comments: 6 pages, revtex

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 40 (1999) 6178-6188

The collective dynamics of solitons with a coset space G/H as moduli space isstudied. It is shown that the collective band for a vibrational state is givenby the inequivalent coset space quantization corresponding to therepresentation of H carried by the vibration.